The Spaniards quickly realized in Hispaniola

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:08.366
that in order to keep things moving forward

00:00:08.366 --> 00:00:10.233
especially to obtain food

00:00:10.233 --> 00:00:13.333
that is, to be able to

00:00:13.600 --> 00:00:14.866
stockpile supplies

00:00:14.866 --> 00:00:16.466
